<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>CollabGlow2 - Deployment Test</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }
        
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: #fff;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 0;
        }
        
        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }
        
        .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }
        
        h2 {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }
        
        .issue-list {
            list-style-type: none;
        }
        
        .issue-list li {
            padding: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .status {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 12px;
            height: 12px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }
        
        .critical {
            background-color: #ff4757;
        }
        
        .warning {
            background-color: #ffa502;
        }
        
        .resolved {
            background-color: #2ed573;
        }
        
        .code-block {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 15px 0;
            overflow-x: auto;
            font-family: monospace;
        }
        
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #fff;
            color: #667eea;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 10px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }
        
        .deploy-steps {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        
        .step {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .step-number {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            background: #fff;
            color: #667eea;
            border-radius: 50%;
            line-height: 40px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 50px;
            padding: 20px;
            opacity: 0.7;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>CollabGlow2 Deployment Analysis</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">Diagnosing Vercel deployment issues for your repository</p>
        </header>
        
        <div class="card">
            <h2>Potential Deployment Issues</h2>
            <ul class="issue-list">
                <li><span class="status critical"></span> Missing package.json file</li>
                <li><span class="status critical"></span> No build script defined</li>
                <li><span class="status warning"></span> Incorrect file paths in HTML</li>
                <li><span class="status warning"></span> Missing vercel.json configuration</li>
                <li><span class="status resolved"></span> Simple HTML structure (not an issue)</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card">
            <h2>Solution</h2>
            <p>Add a package.json file to your repository with the following content:</p>
            
            <div class="code-block">
{
  "name": "collabglow2",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "A collaborative project",
  "scripts": {
    "build": "echo 'No build process needed'"
  },
  "keywords": [],
  "author": "",
  "license": "ISC"
}
            </div>
            
            <p>For more complex projects, you might need a vercel.json file:</p>
            
            <div class="code-block">
{
  "version": 2,
  "builds": [
    {
      "src": "*.html",
      "use": "@vercel/static"
    }
  ],
  "routes": [
    {
      "src": "/(.*)",
      "dest": "/index.html"
    }
  ]
}
            </div>
            
            <a href="https://vercel.com/docs/configuration" class="btn" target="_blank">Vercel Documentation</a>
        </div>
        
        <h2>Deployment Steps</h2>
        <div class="deploy-steps">
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-number">1</div>
                <h3>Add Configuration Files</h3>
                <p>Add package.json and vercel.json to your repository</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-number">2</div>
                <h3>Connect to Vercel</h3>
                <p>Import your GitHub repository in Vercel</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-number">3</div>
                <h3>Deploy</h3>
                <p>Let Vercel automatically deploy your project</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <footer>
        <p>This is a diagnostic page. Add the necessary configuration files to your repository for successful deployment.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
